Podpredseda vl\u225\'e1dy pre ekonomiku doposia\u318\'3e nepredlo\u382\'7eil na verejn\u250\'fa diskusiu, ako sa nakoniec zaviazala vl\u225\'e1da v programovom vyhl\u225\'e1sen\u237\'ed, \u382\'7eiadny nov\u253\'fd syst\u233\'e9m soci\u225\'e1lneho poistenia zahrnuj\u250\'faci syst\u233\'e9m nemocensk\u233\'e9ho poistenia, d\u244\'f4chodkov\u233\'e9ho zabezpe\u269\'0denia a od\u353\'61kod\u328\'48ovania pracovn\u253\'fdch \u250\'farazov a chor\u244\'f4b z povolania.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

