A pre\u269\'0do sa to stalo? Z jednoduch\u233\'e9ho d\u244\'f4vodu. Pri\u353\'61li investi\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 fondy, na ktor\u233\'e9 sme na za\u269\'0diatku upozor\u328\'48ovali, neboli regulovan\u233\'e9 z\u225\'e1konom. A tie investi\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 fondy doniesli \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed, ktor\u237\'ed nemali absol\u250\'fatne \u382\'7eiadne sk\u250\'fasenosti s drev\u225\'e1rskym priemyslom. A jednoducho t\u253\'fdm, \u382\'7ee tam pri\u353\'61li t\u237\'ed \u318\'3eudia, za\u269\'0dali k\u353\'61eftova\u357\'65 o \u250\'faplne in\u253\'fdch veciach. Nestarali sa o rozvoj drev\u225\'e1rskych a n\u225\'e1bytk\u225\'e1rskych podnikov a celul\u243\'f3zovo-papiernick\u233\'e9ho priemyslu. Na v\u253\'fdchode z celul\u243\'f3zovo-papiernick\u233\'e9ho priemyslu - pre ilustr\u225\'e1ciu - Buk\u243\'f3za Vranov, jeden z ve\u318\'3ek\u253\'fdch podnikov. Takisto d\u225\'e1vno v konkurze. \u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee rozumiete, jednozna\u269\'0dne sa uk\u225\'e1zalo, \u382\'7ee kup\u243\'f3nov\u225\'e1 privatiz\u225\'e1cia priniesla v\u253\'fdznamn\u253\'fd kolaps do slovenskej ekonomiky.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
A tento \u269\'0dlovek pokojne si povie, \u382\'7ee on vie nie\u269\'0do o tom, ako spravova\u357\'65 slovensk\u233\'e9 hospod\u225\'e1rstvo. Ve\u271\'0f je to hr\u244\'f4za a strach! \u381\'7diadna sebareflexia! Nepo\u269\'0dul som z jeho \u250\'fast ani raz to\u318\'3eko kritiky, ako napr\u237\'edklad povedal p\u225\'e1n Klaus. P\u225\'e1n Klaus dneska jasne hovor\u237\'ed, \u382\'7ee kup\u243\'f3nov\u225\'e1 privatiz\u225\'e1cia bola hlbok\u253\'fd omyl. Ale u n\u225\'e1s sa o tom e\u353\'61te nepovedalo ani slova. A toto s\u250\'fa d\u244\'f4sledky v tej mikroekonomike, \u382\'7ee dneska v t\u253\'fdch ve\u318\'3ek\u253\'fdch \u269\'0d\u237\'edslach to jednoducho nem\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee vyjs\u357\'65.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
A takto by sme mohli pokra\u269\'0dova\u357\'65, samozrejme, s tou demonopoliz\u225\'e1ciou to postihlo aj po\u318\'3enohospod\u225\'e1rsky, potravin\u225\'e1rsky priemysel ve\u318\'3emi hlboko. Rozpr\u225\'e1valo sa o tom, \u382\'7ee ke\u271\'0f demonopolizujeme v priemysle, tak\u382\'7ee ak\u253\'fdch budeme ma\u357\'65 konkurencieschopn\u253\'fdch v\u253\'fdrobcov. Len\u382\'7ee realita je tak\u225\'e1, \u382\'7ee ke\u271\'0f sem prich\u225\'e1dza Nestl\u233\'e9, ke\u271\'0f sem prich\u225\'e1dzaj\u250\'fa \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ie ve\u318\'3ek\u233\'e9 firmy, napr\u237\'edklad Ikea z tej drev\u225\'e1rskej brand\u382\'7ee at\u271\'0f. - tak \u269\'0do s\u250\'fa to tie na\u353\'61e z\u225\'e1vod\u237\'edky, ktor\u233\'e9 sa tzv. demonopolizovali, konkurencieschopn\u233\'e9 proti t\u253\'fdmto podnikom? Minim\u225\'e1lne.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
Ikea nevyr\u225\'e1bala, ale vyr\u225\'e1ba, lebo vo\u318\'3eakedy v minulosti bolo regulovan\u233\'e9, \u382\'7ee obchodn\u233\'e9 firmy typu Ikea nesm\u250\'fa ma\u357\'65 v\u253\'fdrobn\u250\'fa \u269\'0dinnos\u357\'65, lebo potom bud\u250\'fa zdanen\u233\'e9 in\u253\'fdm sp\u244\'f4sobom. Takto myslela kapitalistick\u225\'e1 ekonomika na obchodn\u233\'e9 firmy typu Ikea. A na\u353\'61i ich pustili do v\u253\'fdrobn\u233\'e9ho p\u244\'f4sobenia, a t\u253\'fdm za\u269\'0d\u237\'ednali vyr\u225\'e1ba\u357\'65 sami pre seba a hraj\u250\'fa sa so ziskami v r\u225\'e1mci svojej firmy a Slovensko zisky ich nikdy neuvid\u237\'ed. \u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee to je pravda o Ikei, ak chcete vedie\u357\'65, p\u225\'e1n kolega, ako to vyzer\u225\'e1 s Ikeou.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
Ale vr\u225\'e1\u357\'65me sa k tomu, \u269\'0do sa \u271\'0falej vyv\u237\'edjalo. Viete ve\u318\'3emi dobre, u\u382\'7e som spom\u237\'ednal, \u382\'7ee prebiehali pod veden\u237\'edm p\u225\'e1na Miklo\u353\'61a aj priame predaje. V akom stave s\u250\'fa podniky, ktor\u233\'e9 sa realizovali v tzv. priamych predajoch p\u225\'e1na Miklo\u353\'61a? Tam sme my \u382\'7eiadali na za\u269\'0diatku, aby jednozna\u269\'0dne sa pred\u225\'e1valo na l\u237\'edzing a aby t\u225\'e1 spl\u225\'e1tka nebola v\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61ia ako 20 %. A aby tie odhady cien boli, pokia\u318\'3e mo\u382\'7eno, \u269\'0do najsubtilnej\u353\'61ie. Ve\u271\'0f viete, \u382\'7ee slovensk\u233\'e9 podniky boli vyhospod\u225\'e1ren\u233\'e9, a ak sa za\u357\'65a\u382\'7eili obrovsk\u253\'fdm n\u225\'e1kladom z predaja, tak t\u237\'ed v\u253\'fdrobcovia jednoducho nemohli investova\u357\'65 do obnovy technol\u243\'f3gi\u237\'ed, do moderniz\u225\'e1cie, do rekon\u353\'61trukcie, lebo museli spl\u225\'e1ca\u357\'65 star\u233\'e9 dl\u382\'7eoby.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
\u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee \u237\'eds\u357\'65 cestou predajov slovensk\u253\'fdm kupuj\u250\'facim s 50-percentnou prvou spl\u225\'e1tkou a s 3-ro\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdm splaten\u237\'edm celej sumy bola vra\u382\'7eda t\u253\'fdch podnikov. Lebo jednoducho tie podniky museli najbli\u382\'7e\u353\'61ie obdobie v\u353\'61etku silu venova\u357\'65 spl\u225\'e1caniu dlhov banke, odkia\u318\'3e si zobrali prv\u253\'fd \u250\'faver na splatenie prvej spl\u225\'e1tky, a spl\u225\'e1canie \u271\'0fal\u353\'61\u237\'edch poh\u318\'3ead\u225\'e1vok vo vz\u357\'65ahu k Fondu n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku. \u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee nebolo v\u244\'f4bec re\u225\'e1lne, aby tieto podniky mohli sledova\u357\'65 zahrani\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd v\u253\'fdvoj a by\u357\'65 konkurencieschopn\u233\'e9 pri otvoren\u237\'ed slovenskej ekonomiky zahrani\u269\'0diu.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
Tam sa dostalo Slovensko pod veden\u237\'edm tak\u253\'fdch teoretick\u253\'fdch pr\u237\'edstupov, ak\u253\'fdch z\u225\'e1stancom bol p\u225\'e1n Miklo\u353\'61. Jednoducho sa slovensk\u225\'e1 ekonomika \u269\'0d\u237\'edm \u271\'0falej z tej nie ve\u318\'3emi dobrej \u353\'61tartovacej poz\u237\'edcie v roku 1989 - 1990 dost\u225\'e1vala do \u271\'0fal\u353\'61\u237\'edch \u357\'65a\u382\'7ekost\u237\'ed spl\u225\'e1can\u237\'edm v\u353\'61elijak\u253\'fdch tak\u253\'fdchto poh\u318\'3ead\u225\'e1vok, ktor\u233\'e9 neviedli k nikomu.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
\u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee ak pri kup\u243\'f3novej privatiz\u225\'e1cii sa majetok vlastne dostal do r\u250\'fak \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed, ktor\u237\'ed s n\u237\'edm nevedeli zach\u225\'e1dza\u357\'65 a vytunelovali ho, cie\u318\'3eavedome, lebo ve\u271\'0f oni sa zaoberali najm\u228\'e4 tunelovan\u237\'edm, a nie v\u253\'fdrobou a predajom svojich v\u253\'fdrobkov, lebo t\u237\'ed v\u353\'61elijak\u237\'ed z\u225\'e1stupcovia fondov ani vo fabrik\u225\'e1ch pov\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61ine neboli, oni to tak len z dia\u318\'3eky sledovali, \u269\'0do sa v tej-ktorej fabrike deje. \u268\'0ces\u357\'65 v\u253\'fdnimk\u225\'e1m, samozrejme. Na Slovensku s\u250\'fa sem-tam aj tak\u233\'e9 podniky, v ktor\u253\'fdch to prebiehalo inak\u353\'61ie, ale s\u250\'fa to naozaj len v\u253\'fdnimky. Ale v t\u253\'fdchto podnikoch, v ktor\u253\'fdch bolo treba spl\u225\'e1ca\u357\'65 tie obrovsk\u233\'e9 poh\u318\'3ead\u225\'e1vky Fondu n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku a bank\u225\'e1m, tak bolo jasn\u233\'e9, \u382\'7ee tieto fabriky skrachovali.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
\u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee toto je v\u253\'fdsledok z minulosti a, samozrejme, musel sa z\u225\'e1konite premietnu\u357\'65 aj do pr\u237\'edtomnosti. Pozrite sa, pre\u269\'0do nie je ochota p\u225\'e1na Miklo\u353\'61a sa zaobera\u357\'65 auditom 116 mld. z b\u225\'e1nk, pre\u269\'0do nie je ochota sa zaobera\u357\'65 d\u244\'f4sledn\u253\'fdm auditom vo Fonde n\u225\'e1rodn\u233\'e9ho majetku, ako to tam vyzer\u225\'e1, a pre\u269\'0do je neochota zaobera\u357\'65 sa anal\u253\'fdzou situ\u225\'e1cie v t\u253\'fdchto podnikoch, ktor\u233\'e9 som menoval. Lebo by vy\u353\'61lo najavo, ak\u253\'fdm sp\u244\'f4sobom on pracoval. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
Ned\u225\'e1vno som bol na n\u225\'e1v\u353\'61teve v jednej z t\u253\'fdchto konsolida\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdch spolo\u269\'0dnost\u237\'ed, hovorili, ako sa tam nar\u225\'e1ba s t\u253\'fdmi poh\u318\'3ead\u225\'e1vkami. Tak si zoberte, \u382\'7ee pr\u237\'edde tam poh\u318\'3ead\u225\'e1vka z banky v hodnote povedzme 100 mil. Sk, v ktorej istina bola mo\u382\'7eno na za\u269\'0diatku nejak\u253\'fdch 80, teraz u\u382\'7e je 100, a nakoniec sa t\u225\'e1 poh\u318\'3ead\u225\'e1vka, ak sa v\u244\'f4bec pred\u225\'e1, ak ten podnik u\u382\'7e neskrachoval a niet ni\u269\'0doho, tak sa pred\u225\'e1 za nejak\u253\'fdch 8 a\u382\'7e 10 %. To v\u353\'61etko ostatn\u233\'e9 zostane ako \u357\'65archa na ob\u269\'0danovi Slovenskej republiky a budeme to uhr\u225\'e1dza\u357\'65 z dan\u237\'ed. \u268\'0co je toto za geni\u225\'e1lna re\u353\'61trukturaliz\u225\'e1cia slovensk\u253\'fdch b\u225\'e1nk?}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
Slovensk\u225\'e1 sporite\u318\'3e\u328\'48a, ktor\u225\'e1 tu u\u382\'7e bola menovan\u225\'e1, sa oddl\u382\'7eila najprv 37 mld. a potom sa predala za 18 mld. No \u269\'0do je to za obchod, kde je strata 19 mld.? Pritom Slovensk\u225\'e1 sporite\u318\'3e\u328\'48a sa oce\u328\'48ovala, ako keby to boli kamene, malta a omietka. Ale Slovensk\u225\'e1 sporite\u318\'3e\u328\'48a, to bola vybudovan\u225\'e1 sie\u357\'65, to bolo know-how, to bolo v\u353\'61etko, \u269\'0do s t\u253\'fdm s\u250\'favis\u237\'ed, a nielen tehly, murivo, bet\u243\'f3n. Ale ocenenie bolo 9,5 mld., mysl\u237\'edm, tak zhruba, predala sa za 18 mld., ale \u250\'faspor obyvate\u318\'3estva tam bolo okolo 200 mld., s ktor\u253\'fdmi t\u237\'edto \u318\'3eudia bud\u250\'fa nar\u225\'e1ba\u357\'65. To je skuto\u269\'0dn\u225\'e1 trhov\u225\'e1 hodnota, ktor\u225\'e1 by sa mala od t\u253\'fdchto \u269\'0d\u237\'edsel odv\u237\'edja\u357\'65. Od \u250\'faspor obyvate\u318\'3estva, ktor\u233\'e9 s\u250\'fa tam, od know-how, od v\u353\'61etk\u233\'e9ho, \u269\'0do s\u250\'favis\u237\'ed s cel\u253\'fdm t\u253\'fdm vybudovan\u237\'edm tej siete. Ve\u271\'0f v\u353\'61etci ve\u318\'3emi dobre vieme, \u382\'7ee slovensk\u233\'e9 obyvate\u318\'3estvo m\u225\'e1 n\u225\'e1vyk odnies\u357\'65 peniaze do sporite\u318\'3ene, \u382\'7ee to bolo budovan\u233\'e9 desiatkami rokov. A toto sa pred\u225\'e1valo predsa! Nie murivo a steny a okn\u225\'e1 a dvere Slovenskej sporite\u318\'3ene. Ale obchodovalo sa tak\u253\'fdmto \u353\'61t\u253\'fdlom.}
