\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
V poslednej dobe sa p\u253\'fd\u353\'61ite t\u253\'fdm, \u382\'7ee s\u250\'fa lacn\u233\'e9 \u250\'faverov\u233\'e9 zdroje. Ale po\u318\'3enohospod\u225\'e1ri ich akosi nedost\u225\'e1vaj\u250\'fa. Nie s\u250\'fa bonitn\u237\'ed. Po\u318\'3enohospod\u225\'e1rske komodity nenach\u225\'e1dzaj\u250\'fa v bankovom sektore nejak\u250\'fa bonitnos\u357\'65, aby sa bankov\u253\'fd sektor trhal o rozd\u225\'e1vanie \u250\'faverov\u253\'fdch zdrojov.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

