Ja si mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee aj to, \u382\'7ee sa neodstr\u225\'e1nila e\u353\'61te cenov\u225\'e1 disparita a na\u271\'0falej sa prehlbuje a najm\u228\'e4 sa prehlbuj\u250\'fa v dosahoch cenov\u233\'e9 no\u382\'7enice na efektivitu po\u318\'3enohospod\u225\'e1rskej v\u253\'fdroby, \u382\'7ee aj to je nie va\u353\'61a spr\u225\'e1vna ekonomick\u225\'e1 politika.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
Ja si mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee to, \u382\'7ee po\u318\'3enohospod\u225\'e1rstvo stratilo potravinov\u250\'fa sebesta\u269\'0dnos\u357\'65 v poslednom obdob\u237\'ed, \u382\'7ee na\u271\'0falej kles\u225\'e1 \u250\'farove\u328\'48 \u382\'7eivo\u269\'0d\u237\'ed\u353\'61nej v\u253\'fdroby, najm\u228\'e4 v stavoch hov\u228\'e4dzieho dobytka, ale aj u o\u353\'61\u237\'edpan\u253\'fdch, \u382\'7ee aj to treba pritvrdi\u357\'65 v tomto rezorte.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
