Na Slovensku v roku 1990, to znamen\u225\'e1 k decembru 1990 bolo 39 603 nezamestnan\u253\'fdch. Potom si pam\u228\'e4t\u225\'e1te, \u382\'7ee v apr\u237\'edli 1991 musel od\u237\'eds\u357\'65 Vladim\u237\'edr Me\u269\'0diar z funkcie, bol od\u237\'edden\u253\'fd, a v decembri 1991 bolo na Slovensku 301 951 nezamestnan\u253\'fdch.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

