\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
\u268\'0co sa t\u253\'fdka \u269\'0diernej pr\u225\'e1ce, aj \u250\'fadaj, ktor\u253\'fd ste povedali, \u382\'7ee sa odhaduje, ak si dobre pam\u228\'e4t\u225\'e1m, 2 a\u382\'7e 8 % \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed odhaduje Eur\u243\'f3pska komisia, \u225\'e1no, to kore\u353\'61ponduje s t\u253\'fdmi odhadmi, ktor\u233\'e9 m\u225\'e1me aj my, aj ke\u271\'0f sk\u244\'f4r v tom vy\u353\'61\u353\'61om horizonte, vo vy\u353\'61\u353\'61om limite a sved\u269\'0d\u237\'ed to o tom, \u382\'7ee priestor tam je a \u382\'7ee s\u250\'fa potrebn\u233\'e9 omnoho razantnej\u353\'61ie opatrenia. Neraz som povedal aj na tejto p\u244\'f4de, \u382\'7ee ani ja s\u225\'e1m, ani vl\u225\'e1da nie sme spokojn\u237\'ed s t\u253\'fdm, ako sa \u250\'fa\u269\'0dinn\u233\'e9 opatrenia v tejto oblasti urobili, a preto sme sa k tejto t\u233\'e9me znovu vr\u225\'e1tili na v\u253\'fdjazdovom zasadnut\u237\'ed v Ko\u353\'61iciach, ke\u271\'0f p\u244\'f4vodne prijat\u233\'e9 opatrenia, ktor\u233\'e9 boli prijat\u233\'e9 predt\u253\'fdm v Pre\u353\'61ove, neboli dostato\u269\'0dne efekt\u237\'edvne a dostato\u269\'0dne re\u225\'e1lne.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
\u268\'0co sa t\u253\'fdka re\u225\'e1lnych miezd, dovo\u318\'3ete mi poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee, samozrejme, uvedomujeme si, \u382\'7ee do\u353\'61lo k poklesu re\u225\'e1lnych miezd, \u382\'7ee do\u353\'61lo k poklesu \u382\'7eivotnej \u250\'farovne a nikoho z n\u225\'e1s to nete\u353\'61\u237\'ed. My sme ale jasne povedali na za\u269\'0diatku, \u382\'7ee stabiliz\u225\'e1cia ekonomiky bude nies\u357\'65 so sebou aj do\u269\'0dasn\u233\'e9 zn\u237\'ed\u382\'7eenie \u382\'7eivotnej \u250\'farovne. D\u244\'f4le\u382\'7eit\u233\'e9 je poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee keby sa tieto stabiliza\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 opatrenia nerobili, potom by tieto n\u225\'e1klady, soci\u225\'e1lne n\u225\'e1klady z h\u318\'3eadiska zn\u237\'ed\u382\'7eenia \u382\'7eivotnej \u250\'farovne, zn\u237\'ed\u382\'7eenia re\u225\'e1lnych miezd boli r\u225\'e1dovo vy\u353\'61\u353\'61ie, ako boli tie, ktor\u233\'e9 sme museli nies\u357\'65.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af7\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4

